{"tid":2425223,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"杜汶澤力挺台農「品質不比日本差」　呼籲香港人：支持台灣鳳梨！","createTime":"2021-02-27T08:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T13:36:56.000Z","uid":16659,"like":65,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3ea49a3d342f61571dfe44d82980d10ff3ebbde0","tid":2425223,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:08:58.000Z","msg":"大陸25日透過「海峽兩岸農產品檢疫檢驗合作協議」平台，通知因台灣鳳梨多次檢出介殼蟲，將自3月1日起暫停我方鳳梨輸入，引發各界熱議。對此，香港男星杜汶澤就發聲力挺，更呼籲香港民眾一起支持台灣鳳梨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5475/d5475030.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5475%2Fd5475030.jpg&h=f77accf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲港星杜汶澤政治立場鮮明。（圖／翻攝自Facebook／杜汶澤）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤近年因為經常關注香港社會運動，遭到大陸封殺，而大陸宣布將於3月1日起暫停台灣的鳳梨輸入，他也公開呼籲香港人一起力挺台灣，他表示如果想支持台灣的鳳梨，但是買不到的話，可以改買台灣出產的鳳梨酥、鳳梨乾，希望大家能夠同舟共濟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5475/5475031.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5475%2F5475031.jpg&h=b5303e08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲杜汶澤呼籲香港人力挺台農。（圖／翻攝自Facebook／杜汶澤）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤更直言：「其實只要你去過台灣，都會知道當地農產品品質之高不下於日本！這是多年來台農努力和政府支持的成果。」他透露自己將出產台灣麻辣鴨血之外，還會繼續積極研究，把自己認為最好的農產品從台灣進口到香港，「支持台農之餘，又可享用高品質健康又美味的食品，win win 雙贏！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5475/5475032.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5475%2F5475032.jpg&h=3bbf39eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲杜汶澤大讚台灣農產品品質。（圖／翻攝自Facebook／杜汶澤）"},{"pid":"8d7785e40f212886a9b64e414891704f25721e30","tid":2425223,"uid":113073,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:12:00.000Z","msg":"其實日本有冇鳳梨<br />\n<br />\n台灣鳳梨又平又正又冇渣，唔那口<br />\n<br />\n去買仲會幫你切埋<br />\n<br />\n成日都自己一個買一個食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dec6968247073fc1c5758d13eae29a49dc6296c","tid":2425223,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:13:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28774b67ffea3692f25eb9dba60509b89595335e","tid":2425223,"uid":69083,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:13:28.000Z","msg":"菠蘿好食d，定鳳梨好食d"},{"pid":"529b7f5437d14d612e54d41682216ad38d11987b","tid":2425223,"uid":57513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:13:32.000Z","msg":"邊度有得買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bca6862d49a1a4c6af0629724c6d54138c74be3","tid":2425223,"uid":11694,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:14:24.000Z","msg":"台灣波蘿超好食喎，普通牛奶波蘿都已經好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97781722ed285785de7548f6374d744a6239e571","tid":2425223,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28774b67ffea3692f25eb9dba60509b89595335e","tid":2425223,"uid":69083,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:13:28.000Z","msg":"菠蘿好食d，定鳳梨好食d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:15:09.000Z","msg":"why not both<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c7775eb2731d310724a61d87df2c4dad928058","tid":2425223,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:23:40.000Z","msg":"想去台灣了...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d7ab3ac1579f837d57132603b80527ebd6ad2e0","tid":2425223,"uid":231883,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:26:11.000Z","msg":"其實台灣d農產品都好正，但唔知係政治因素定技術問題，出口無其他國家咁多，係台灣以